</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>PS 將進一步整合 Discord　可於 Discord 顯示自己正在玩的遊戲</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/02/playstation-discord-account-connection-linking-game/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=playstation-discord-account-connection-linking-game</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[藍骨]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 02 Feb 2022 08:22:34 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[Discord]]></category><category><![CDATA[playstation]]></category><category><![CDATA[SONY]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1084469</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Discord 是不少遊戲玩家都喜歡使用的社群平台，而如果可以在家用遊戲機上也整合平台功能，確實更加方便。最近 Sony 就將會在 PS 上整合 Discord 功能，可以在 Discord 上顯示遊玩狀態。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Discord 是不少遊戲玩家都喜歡使用的社群平台，而如果可以在家用遊戲機上也整合平台功能，確實更加方便。最近 Sony 就將會在 PS 上整合 Discord 功能，可以在 Discord 上顯示遊玩狀態。<br /><span id="more-1084469"></span></p><p>Discord 在最近一個網址上公佈指，用家將可以在平台上將帳戶連接至 PSN，在遊玩 PlayStation 4 或 PlayStation 5 遊戲時，其 PSN ID 和遊戲狀態將可以在 Discord 上自動顯示，這樣一來在 Discord 上的朋友也可以快速看到 PSN ID 並加為好友。</p><p><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61f30cd0389f9e6e968368a5_G-2huHi3KZtZm-W_6k5wR-aAtvoXNSK31Q6cp571U2BL9L7fmNbY1emqGGtiJ3z8Jo8DoWVm81gVqXQ8z5mEijWcRdAl5ctsICxNrIGutIyZo83OSckgycx7H6rVCrEHe7WW8r3z.jpeg" alt="" width="1600" height="900" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1084494" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61f30cd0389f9e6e968368a5_G-2huHi3KZtZm-W_6k5wR-aAtvoXNSK31Q6cp571U2BL9L7fmNbY1emqGGtiJ3z8Jo8DoWVm81gVqXQ8z5mEijWcRdAl5ctsICxNrIGutIyZo83OSckgycx7H6rVCrEHe7WW8r3z.jpeg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61f30cd0389f9e6e968368a5_G-2huHi3KZtZm-W_6k5wR-aAtvoXNSK31Q6cp571U2BL9L7fmNbY1emqGGtiJ3z8Jo8DoWVm81gVqXQ8z5mEijWcRdAl5ctsICxNrIGutIyZo83OSckgycx7H6rVCrEHe7WW8r3z-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61f30cd0389f9e6e968368a5_G-2huHi3KZtZm-W_6k5wR-aAtvoXNSK31Q6cp571U2BL9L7fmNbY1emqGGtiJ3z8Jo8DoWVm81gVqXQ8z5mEijWcRdAl5ctsICxNrIGutIyZo83OSckgycx7H6rVCrEHe7WW8r3z-1280x720.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61f30cd0389f9e6e968368a5_G-2huHi3KZtZm-W_6k5wR-aAtvoXNSK31Q6cp571U2BL9L7fmNbY1emqGGtiJ3z8Jo8DoWVm81gVqXQ8z5mEijWcRdAl5ctsICxNrIGutIyZo83OSckgycx7H6rVCrEHe7WW8r3z-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61f30cd0389f9e6e968368a5_G-2huHi3KZtZm-W_6k5wR-aAtvoXNSK31Q6cp571U2BL9L7fmNbY1emqGGtiJ3z8Jo8DoWVm81gVqXQ8z5mEijWcRdAl5ctsICxNrIGutIyZo83OSckgycx7H6rVCrEHe7WW8r3z-1536x864.jpeg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61f30cd115459d5c5e65cee7_b3O7BEiZs8FgFtzrFcJrE4Mk05b-IYkFD8VMqP2tKcNFJvMq7CrfalBR9951Ka2pm-8wkh2UrAKX6LiftbxDMNozskI0SuTc6kn_VWiisrHk80TOX16zUs_au74u9OE0kszbv7v.jpeg" alt="" width="1600" height="900" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1084495" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61f30cd115459d5c5e65cee7_b3O7BEiZs8FgFtzrFcJrE4Mk05b-IYkFD8VMqP2tKcNFJvMq7CrfalBR9951Ka2pm-8wkh2UrAKX6LiftbxDMNozskI0SuTc6kn_VWiisrHk80TOX16zUs_au74u9OE0kszbv7v.jpeg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61f30cd115459d5c5e65cee7_b3O7BEiZs8FgFtzrFcJrE4Mk05b-IYkFD8VMqP2tKcNFJvMq7CrfalBR9951Ka2pm-8wkh2UrAKX6LiftbxDMNozskI0SuTc6kn_VWiisrHk80TOX16zUs_au74u9OE0kszbv7v-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61f30cd115459d5c5e65cee7_b3O7BEiZs8FgFtzrFcJrE4Mk05b-IYkFD8VMqP2tKcNFJvMq7CrfalBR9951Ka2pm-8wkh2UrAKX6LiftbxDMNozskI0SuTc6kn_VWiisrHk80TOX16zUs_au74u9OE0kszbv7v-1280x720.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61f30cd115459d5c5e65cee7_b3O7BEiZs8FgFtzrFcJrE4Mk05b-IYkFD8VMqP2tKcNFJvMq7CrfalBR9951Ka2pm-8wkh2UrAKX6LiftbxDMNozskI0SuTc6kn_VWiisrHk80TOX16zUs_au74u9OE0kszbv7v-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61f30cd115459d5c5e65cee7_b3O7BEiZs8FgFtzrFcJrE4Mk05b-IYkFD8VMqP2tKcNFJvMq7CrfalBR9951Ka2pm-8wkh2UrAKX6LiftbxDMNozskI0SuTc6kn_VWiisrHk80TOX16zUs_au74u9OE0kszbv7v-1536x864.jpeg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>Sony 早在去年就宣佈與 Discord 建立合作夥伴關係，整合雙方的服務。而目前雖然 PS 上仍然未推出原生的 Discord App，但在社交功能上的整合，看來也是一個實用的發展方向。而另一方面 Xbox 系列就早已整合部分 Discord 功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61f19792d9080128ab9a46b9_VQ60TskTILNPUY0L6KGZNZ0jflAmC4bq_vigu_lyBPti_BzMp-EpJUpBXh9WFObNaPzNzYe2ZOYkga_F1rk-qRFJVHLUCSiaO0wIjkzMdqLZ_VASpinMawA4UKq0IyhG2ZyzpJ4P.jpeg" alt="" width="1200" height="1294" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1084496" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61f19792d9080128ab9a46b9_VQ60TskTILNPUY0L6KGZNZ0jflAmC4bq_vigu_lyBPti_BzMp-EpJUpBXh9WFObNaPzNzYe2ZOYkga_F1rk-qRFJVHLUCSiaO0wIjkzMdqLZ_VASpinMawA4UKq0IyhG2ZyzpJ4P.jpeg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61f19792d9080128ab9a46b9_VQ60TskTILNPUY0L6KGZNZ0jflAmC4bq_vigu_lyBPti_BzMp-EpJUpBXh9WFObNaPzNzYe2ZOYkga_F1rk-qRFJVHLUCSiaO0wIjkzMdqLZ_VASpinMawA4UKq0IyhG2ZyzpJ4P-538x580.jpeg 538w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61f19792d9080128ab9a46b9_VQ60TskTILNPUY0L6KGZNZ0jflAmC4bq_vigu_lyBPti_BzMp-EpJUpBXh9WFObNaPzNzYe2ZOYkga_F1rk-qRFJVHLUCSiaO0wIjkzMdqLZ_VASpinMawA4UKq0IyhG2ZyzpJ4P-835x900.jpeg 835w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61f19792d9080128ab9a46b9_VQ60TskTILNPUY0L6KGZNZ0jflAmC4bq_vigu_lyBPti_BzMp-EpJUpBXh9WFObNaPzNzYe2ZOYkga_F1rk-qRFJVHLUCSiaO0wIjkzMdqLZ_VASpinMawA4UKq0IyhG2ZyzpJ4P-768x828.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>來源：<a href="https://discord.com/blog/playstation-discord-account-connection-linking-game-status">Discord</a></p>
